export enum ColorString {
  primary = "#d65780",
  secondary = "#496ddb",
  white = "#fff",
  black = "#000",
  transparent = "transparent",
  grey = "#CCCCCC",
  lightGrey = "#C4C4C4",
  primaryGrey = "#8A8A8E",
  schmoozGreen = "#3DDC97",
  red = "#FF495C",
  yellow = "#F4D35E",
  info = "#256EFF",
  destructive = "#FF495C",
  warning = "#F4D35E",
}

export type ColorPaletteStrings = keyof ColorString;
